<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />实在是太厉害了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />喔！<delay8 />我等很久啦！！<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶嘿嘿，<delay20 />现在才刚开始，<delay8 />
