再保存体力啦！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一起尽情奔跑吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="3" />，你在看吗？<delay frames="30" />
