<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过要是韧带过于紧绷就不太好啦！
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />烟花的声响这么大，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有听见我说话吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />烟花最棒！！<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶嘿嘿，<delay20 />我要是从丹田发力大声喊的话，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不输给烟花的声响哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="10" b="12" /><anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 /><size value="150" />好！<delay20 />再来！<size value="100" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～<delay8 />啊～<delay20 /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大声喊叫之后嗓子干干的。<delay frames="40" />
