又大又华丽的烟花，<delay8 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可真大方啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">烟花马上就要放完了，<delay20 />
