	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？！<delay20 />已经是这个时间了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花马上就要放完了呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，全力以赴到最后一刻
